@atahabaki:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/16924] fixed str expand to not consider two dots outside curly braces as range operator (#16924)
@ysthakur:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/16914] set HOME for test_config_path tests (#16914)
@Bahex:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/16912] added more granular type widening and stricter type checking (#16912)
